PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Energy, Mines and Resources of Jean Demers, of Outremont, Quebec, as a director of the Atomic Energy of Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jean Vacchino, whose term has expired.
